{"type":"message","id":"ce22213d","parentId":"99d06482","timestamp":"2026-06-03T18:44:09.648Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我看到代码已经尝试获取 `device_name`。问题可能是：\n1. API `/api/v1/devices/{ip}/info` 返回的数据结构不对\n2. 或者 WASM 登录后没有更新 `connectedDevice`\n\n让我检查 WASM SDK 登录成功后是否能从设备获取 OSD 名称。OSD 名称通常通过 ISAPI `/ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/name` 获取。\n\n先看 `getDisplayName` 函数当前的逻辑："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-23b2b2e88fd44c68bd6707e3448f1e61","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":20,"offset":2148,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":33217,"output":141,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33358,"cost":{"input":0.033216999999999997,"output":0.0004512,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.033668199999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780512240514,"responseId":"cht000de5a2@dx19e8eccb88ab828282"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0445441e","parentId":"ce22213d","timestamp":"2026-06-03T18:44:09.655Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-23b2b2e88fd44c68bd6707e3448f1e61","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        var status = document.getElementById('deviceStatus');\r\n        var wsDot = document.getElementById('wsDot');\r\n        var wsStatus = document.getElementById('wsStatus');\r\n        \r\n        var connected = window.connectedDevice;\r\n        \r\n        // 获取显示名称：优先用户自定义名称，其次型号，最后 IP\r\n        function getDisplayName(dev) {\r\n            if (!dev) return '未知设备';\r\n            // name 是用户自定义名称\r\n            if (dev.name && dev.name.trim()) return dev.name.trim();\r\n            // device_name 是设备返回的名称\r\n            if (dev.device_name && dev.device_name.trim()) return dev.device_name.trim();\r\n            // 最后用 IP\r\n            return dev.ip || '未知设备';\r\n        }\r\n        \r\n        // 更新左侧设备状态\r\n        if (dot && status) {\r\n            if (connected) {\r\n\n[41 more lines in file. Use offset=2168 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780512249655}}
{"type":"message","id":"6d410c29","parentId":"0445441e","timestamp":"2026-06-03T18:44:16.327Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在让我在 WASM 登录成功后获取 OSD 设备名称。海康摄像机的 OSD 设备名称通过 ISAPI `/ISAPI/System/Video/inputs/channels/{channelID}` 获取。\n\n最小限度修复：在 `clickLogin2` 登录成功后，获取 OSD 名称并更新 `connectedDevice.device_name`。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-13fb3323f6dd490a9ed3be8451ab910e","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":1988,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":33547,"output":116,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33663,"cost":{"input":0.033547,"output":0.0003712,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0339182}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780512249656,"responseId":"cht000de785@dx19e8eccdf1cb828282"}}
{"type":"message","id":"573c96ef","parentId":"6d410c29","timestamp":"2026-06-03T18:44:16.334Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-13fb3323f6dd490a9ed3be8451ab910e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    // 博客方案：I_Login\r\n    WebVideoCtrl.I_Login(szIP, 1, szPort, szUsername, szPassword, {\r\n        timeout: 5000,\r\n        success: function(xmlDoc) {\r\n            g_bLoggedIn2 = true;\r\n            g_szDeviceIdentify2 = szIP + '_' + szPort;\r\n            console.log('[WASM SDK] Login success: ' + g_szDeviceIdentify2);\r\n            if (typeof ptzLog === 'function') ptzLog(szIP + ' 登录成功！', 'success');\r\n            \r\n            // 博客方案：延迟500ms后执行 getDevicePort + getChannelInfo\r\n            setTimeout(() => {\r\n                // Step 1: getDevicePort\r\n                var oPort = WebVideoCtrl.I_GetDevicePort(g_szDeviceIdentify2);\r\n                console.log('[WASM SDK] GetDevicePort:', oPort);\r\n                if (oPort) {\r\n                    g_iRtspPort2 = oPort.iRtspPort || 554;\r\n                    g_iWebSocketPort = oPort.iWebSocketPort || 7681;\r\n                    if (typeof ptzLog === 'function') ptzLog('WebSocket端口: ' + g_iWebSocketPort, 'info');\r\n                    document.cookie = 'webVideoCtrlProxyWs=' + szIP + ':' + g_iWebSocketPort + '; path=/';\r\n                    document.cookie = 'webVideoCtrlProxyWsChannel=101; path=/';\r\n                }\r\n                \r\n                // Step 1.5: 异步获取 token 修复 szAuth（同步XHR被弃用）\r\n                var deviceSet = WebVideoCtrl.w_deviceSet;\r\n                var device = deviceSet && deviceSet.length > 0 ? deviceSet[0] : null;\r\n                var tokenPromise = Promise.resolve();\r\n                if (device && !device.szAuth) {\r\n                    console.log('[WASM SDK] szAuth empty, fetching token async...');\r\n                    tokenPromise = fetch('/ISAPI/Security/token?format=json', {credentials:'include'})\r\n                        .then(function(r) { return r.json(); })\r\n                        .then(function(data) {\r\n                            if (data && data.Token && data.Token.value) {\r\n                                device.szAuth = data.Token.value;\r\n                                console.log('[WASM SDK] szAuth set async:', device.szAuth.substring(0,16) + '...');\r\n                                if (typeof ptzLog === 'function') ptzLog('Token获取成功', 'success');\r\n                            }\r\n                        })\r\n                        .catch(function(e) { console.log('[WASM SDK] Token fetch failed:', e); });\r\n                }\r\n                \r\n                tokenPromise.then(function() {\r\n                getChannelInfo().then(function() {\r\n                    console.log('[WASM SDK] 获取通道结束');\r\n                    clickStartRealPlay({ iStreamType: 2 });\r\n                }).catch(function(err) {\r\n                    console.log('[WASM SDK] 获取通道失败: ' + err);\r\n                    g_iChannelID = 1;\r\n                    clickStartRealPlay({ iStreamType: 2 });\r\n                });\r\n                }); // end tokenPromise.then\r\n\n[171 more lines in file. Use offset=2038 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780512256334}}
