{"type":"message","id":"c2967798","parentId":"0c67fcea","timestamp":"2026-06-03T18:45:33.373Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"让我看 `refreshDevices` 函数和 API 返回的数据结构："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-f2e896fb19a343b09215826ad98c1790","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":1122,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":36204,"output":59,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36263,"cost":{"input":0.036204,"output":0.0001888,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0363928}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780512329673,"responseId":"cht000f09d2@dx19e8ece10efb8ab592"}}
{"type":"message","id":"84ba11d4","parentId":"c2967798","timestamp":"2026-06-03T18:45:33.382Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-f2e896fb19a343b09215826ad98c1790","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        function refreshDevices() {\r\n            console.log('[REFRESH] refreshDevices called');\r\n            return apiGet('/api/v1/devices').then(function(result) {\r\n                console.log('[REFRESH] API response:', result);\r\n                if (!result.success) {\r\n                    allDevices = [];\r\n                    renderDevices([]);\r\n                    return;\r\n                }\r\n                allDevices = result.data || [];\r\n                renderDevices(allDevices);\r\n                // Update dashboard counters\r\n                var online = allDevices.filter(function(d) { return d.online; }).length;\r\n                var countEl = document.getElementById('devCount');\r\n                if (countEl) countEl.textContent = allDevices.length;\r\n                var onlineEl = document.getElementById('devOnline');\r\n                if (onlineEl) onlineEl.textContent = online;\r\n                var totalEl = document.getElementById('devTotal');\r\n                if (totalEl) totalEl.textContent = allDevices.length;\r\n                // Update PTZ & advanced device dropdowns\r\n                refreshPtzDeviceList();\r\n                refreshAdvancedDeviceSelectors();\r\n            }).catch(function(e) {\r\n                console.warn('Failed to refresh devices:', e);\r\n            });\r\n        }\r\n        function renderDevices(devices) {\r\n            var tb = document.getElementById('deviceTable');\r\n            if (!tb) return;\r\n            if (!devices.length) {\r\n                tb.innerHTML = '<tr><td colspan=\"8\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#6e7681\">暂无设备</td></tr>';\r\n                return;\r\n            }\r\n            var html = devices.map(function(d) {\r\n                var sourceBadge = d.source === 'sadp'\r\n                    ? '<span class=\"badge sadp\">SADP</span>'\r\n                    : '<span class=\"badge manual\">手动</span>';\r\n                var onlineBadge = d.online\r\n                    ? '<span class=\"badge online\">在线</span>'\r\n                    : '<span class=\"badge offline\">离线</span>';\r\n                var actions = buildDeviceActions(d);\r\n                return '<tr>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + sourceBadge + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.mac || '--') + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.ip || '--') + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.gateway || '--') + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.name || d.device_name || '--') + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + (d.model || '--') + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + onlineBadge + '</td>'\r\n                    + '<td>' + actions + '</td>'\r\n\n[1037 more lines in file. Use offset=1172 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780512333382}}
{"type":"message","id":"f15efcec","parentId":"84ba11d4","timestamp":"2026-06-03T18:45:48.134Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"设备列表从 `/api/v1/devices` 获取，数据包含 `name` 和 `device_name`。\n\n现在看设置 `connectedDevice` 的地方，确认是否正确传递了这些字段："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ca46327b9c6a4d73bb297429","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":257,"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\index.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":36873,"output":86,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36959,"cost":{"input":0.036872999999999996,"output":0.0002752,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0371482}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780512333383,"responseId":"cht000de655@dx19e8ece1f6cb87e692"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b79f30b6","parentId":"f15efcec","timestamp":"2026-06-03T18:45:48.140Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ca46327b9c6a4d73bb297429","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                        if (!window.connectedDevice && allDevices && allDevices.length > 0) {\r\n                            // Priority: 1) last connected MAC, 2) any online device\r\n                            var onlineDev = lastMac ? allDevices.find(function(d) { return d.mac === lastMac && d.online; }) : null;\r\n                            if (!onlineDev) onlineDev = allDevices.find(function(d) { return d.online; });\r\n                            if (onlineDev) {\r\n                                // Fetch credentials and set window.connectedDevice\r\n                                apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/devices/' + onlineDev.ip + '/credentials').then(function(creds) {\r\n                                    if (creds && creds.success) {\r\n                                        window.connectedDevice = {\r\n                                            ip: onlineDev.ip,\r\n                                            model: onlineDev.model || '',\r\n                                            name: onlineDev.name || onlineDev.device_name || '',\r\n                                            mac: onlineDev.mac || '',\r\n                                            username: creds.username || 'admin',\r\n                                            password: creds.password || '',\r\n                                            port: creds.port || 80,\r\n                                            online: true\r\n                                        };\r\n                                        // Save MAC to localStorage for memory\r\n                                        if (onlineDev.mac) localStorage.setItem('lastConnectedMac', onlineDev.mac);\r\n                                        // Fetch device name if not available\r\n                                        if (!window.connectedDevice.name) {\r\n                                            apiGet('/api/v1/devices/' + onlineDev.ip + '/info').then(function(info) {\r\n                                                if (info && info.success && info.data && info.data.device_name) {\r\n                                                    window.connectedDevice.name = info.data.device_name;\r\n                                                    if (window.updateDeviceStatus) window.updateDeviceStatus();\r\n                                                }\r\n                                            });\r\n                                        }\r\n                                        if (window.clickLogin2) { window.clickLogin2(); }\r\n\n[1922 more lines in file. Use offset=287 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780512348140}}
{"type":"message","id":"8112ba36","parentId":"b79f30b6","timestamp":"2026-06-03T18:45:57.108Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看到问题了！当前逻辑：\n```javascript\nname: onlineDev.name || onlineDev.device_name || '',\n```\n\n这把 `device_name` 合并到 `name` 里了。但老板要求的优先级是：\n1. `name`（用户自定义）\n2. `device_name`（OSD 名称）\n3. `ip`\n\n当前代码把两者合并成一个字段，导致无法区分。\n\n最小限度修复：分开存储 `name` 和 `device_name`，让 `getDisplayName` 函数正确处理优先级。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-b2dc6fefc73144be953d8bbbe647725e","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"                                        window.connectedDevice = {\n                                            ip: onlineDev.ip,\n                                            model: onlineDev.model || '',\n                                            name: onlineDev.name || '',\n                                            device_name: onlineDev.device_name || '',\n                                            mac: onlineDev.mac || '',\n                                            username: creds.username || 'admin',\n                                            password: creds.password || '',\n                                            port: creds.port || 80,\n                                            online: true\n                                        };","oldText":"                                        window.connectedDevice = {\n                                            ip: onlineDev.ip,\n                                            model: onlineDev.model || '',\n                                            name: onlineDev.name || onlineDev.device_name || '',\n                                            mac: onlineDev.mac || '',\n                                            username: creds.username || 'admin',\n                                            password: creds.password || '',\n                                            port: creds.port || 80,\n                                            online: true\n         