{"type":"message","id":"29264150","parentId":"738ead5a","timestamp":"2026-06-03T19:49:20.408Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"开发完成。**汇报结果**：\n\n---\n\n## 开发完成 ✅\n\n### 文件结构\n\n```\nastrohub/\n├── calibrate/\n│   ├── __init__.py\n│   ├── core/\n│   │   ├── __init__.py\n│   │   ├── coordinates.py     # RA/DEC ↔ Alt/Az 坐标转换\n│   │   ├── star_catalog.py    # 亮星星表 (50颗)\n│   │   ├── plate_solve.py     # ASTAP 调用封装\n│   │   └── model.py           # T-Point 误差模型\n│   ├── image/                  # 解析图像存储\n│   ├── history/                # 校准历史记录\n│   ├── calibration_manual.py   # 方案一：手动校准\n│   ├── calibration_auto.py     # 方案二：自动解析\n│   ├── calibration_store.py    # 结果存储\n│   └── router.py               # REST API (15个端点)\n├── config/                     # 校准参数存储\n└── documents/\n    └── DEVELOPMENT_PLAN.md     # 开发文档\n```\n\n### API 端点 (15个)\n\n| 端点 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| `GET /api/v1/calibrate/status` | 系统状态 |\n| `GET /api/v1/calibrate/devices` | 已校准设备列表 |\n| `POST /api/v1/calibrate/start` | 开始校准 |\n| `GET /api/v1/calibrate/session/{device_ip}` | 会话状态 |\n| `POST /api/v1/calibrate/select_star` | 选择恒星(手动) |\n| `POST /api/v1/calibrate/record` | 记录校准点(手动) |\n| `POST /api/v1/calibrate/capture` | 拍摄解析(自动) |\n| `POST /api/v1/calibrate/compute` | 计算参数 |\n| `POST /api/v1/calibrate/save` | 保存结果 |\n| `POST /api/v1/calibrate/reset` | 重置校准 |\n| `GET /api/v1/calibrate/stars/visible` | 可见亮星 |\n| `GET /api/v1/calibrate/stars/recommended` | 推荐校准星 |\n\n### 依赖项\n\n```\nastropy  # 坐标转换 (可选，无则用简化算法)\nnumpy    # 最小二乘拟合\nfastapi  # API 路由\n```\n\n### 待集成\n\n需要在主服务 `main.py` 中注册路由：\n\n```python\nfrom calibrate.router import router as calibrate_router\napp.include_router(calibrate_router)\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":90742,"output":581,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91323,"cost":{"input":0.09074199999999999,"output":0.0018592,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0926012}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780516146836,"responseId":"cht000ddf74@dx19e8f084ff1b85f532"}}
