{"type":"message","id":"7dc58416","parentId":"7cbf4a63","timestamp":"2026-06-03T20:16:33.086Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_265f8ede52b9435087a1e109","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!-- 高级功能页面 - v5.31 左中右布局 -->\n<div class=\"page\" id=\"page-advanced\">\n    <div class=\"adv-layout\">\n        <!-- 左侧：测试项目 (25%) -->\n        <div class=\"adv-left\">\n            <div class=\"adv-section-title\">测试项目</div>\n            <div class=\"adv-menu\">\n                <button class=\"adv-menu-item active\" data-test=\"function\" onclick=\"selectAdvTest('function')\">\n                    <span class=\"menu-icon\">🔍</span>\n                    <span>功能测试</span>\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"adv-menu-item\" data-test=\"limit\" onclick=\"selectAdvTest('limit')\">\n                    <span class=\"menu-icon\">📐</span>\n                    <span>限位测试</span>\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"adv-menu-item\" data-test=\"speed\" onclick=\"selectAdvTest('speed')\">\n                    <span class=\"menu-icon\">⚡</span>\n                    <span>速度测试</span>\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"adv-menu-item\" data-test=\"stream\" onclick=\"selectAdvTest('stream')\">\n                    <span class=\"menu-icon\">📡</span>\n                    <span>推流/存储</span>\n                </button>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"adv-section-title\" style=\"margin-top:16px\">操作</div>\n            <div class=\"adv-actions\">\n                <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-block\" id=\"btnAdvRun\" onclick=\"runAdvTest()\">▶ 开始测试</button>\n                <button class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-block\" id=\"btnAdvStop\" onclick=\"stopAdvTest()\" disabled>⏹ 停止</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 中间：实时画面 (55%) -->\n        <div class=\"adv-center\">\n            <div class=\"adv-section-title\">实时画面</div>\n            <div class=\"adv-video-box\" id=\"advVideoBox\">\n                <div id=\"advVideoPlaceholder\">\n                    <div style=\"color:#6e7681;text-align:center;padding:40px\">\n                        <div style=\"font-size:48px;margin-bottom:16px\">📹</div>\n                        <div id=\"advVideoStatus\">连接设备后显示实时画面</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- 右侧：测试输出 (20%) -->\n        <div class=\"adv-right\">\n            <div class=\"adv-section-title\">测试输出</div>\n            <div class=\"adv-output\" id=\"advOutput\">\n                <div class=\"output-line info\">系统就绪</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"adv-section-title\" style=\"margin-top:8px\">测试结果</div>\n            <div class=\"adv-result\" id=\"advResult\">\n                <div style=\"color:#6e7681;text-align:center;padding:20px\">\n                    测试结果将在此显示\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n/* 高级功能 v5.31 布局 */\n.adv-layout {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 0;\n    min-height: calc(100vh - 120px);\n    background: #0d1117;\n}\n\n.adv-left {\n    width: 25%;\n    min-width: 200px;\n    background: #161b22;\n    border-right: 1px solid #21262d;\n    padding: 12px;\n}\n\n.adv-center {\n    width: 55%;\n    padding: 12px;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n}\n\n.adv-right {\n    width: 20%;\n    min-width: 240px;\n    background: #161b22;\n    border-left: 1px solid #21262d;\n    padding: 12px;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n}\n\n.adv-section-title {\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #8b949e;\n    padding: 8px 0;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #21262d;\n\n[264 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780517793086}}
{"type":"message","id":"d9968aa2","parentId":"7dc58416","timestamp":"2026-06-03T20:16:49.694Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"高级功能页面目前有：功能测试、限位测试、速度测试、推流/存储。\n\n我开发的天文校准是**新增功能**，应该作为新的测试项目添加到高级功能页面。\n\n让我添加天文校准入口："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-e8ce148f207e4bcf8fafcb5be6293933","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"            <div class=\"adv-menu\">\n                <button class=\"adv-menu-item active\" data-test=\"function\" onclick=\"selectAdvTest('function')\">\n                    <span class=\"menu-icon\">🔍</span>\n                    <span>功能测试</span>\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"adv-menu-item\" data-test=\"limit\" onclick=\"selectAdvTest('limit')\">\n                    <span class=\"menu-icon\">📐</span>\n                    <span>限位测试</span>\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"adv-menu-item\" data-test=\"speed\" onclick=\"selectAdvTest('speed')\">\n                    <span class=\"menu-icon\">⚡</span>\n                    <span>速度测试</span>\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"adv-menu-item\" data-test=\"stream\" onclick=\"selectAdvTest('stream')\">\n                    <span class=\"menu-icon\">📡</span>\n                    <span>推流/存储</span>\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"adv-menu-item\" data-test=\"astrocal\" onclick=\"selectAdvTest('astrocal')\">\n                    <span class=\"menu-icon\">🌟</span>\n                    <span>天文校准</span>\n                </button>\n            </div>","oldText":"            <div class=\"adv-menu\">\n                <button class=\"adv-menu-item active\" data-test=\"function\" onclick=\"selectAdvTest('function')\">\n                    <span class=\"menu-icon\">🔍</span>\n                    <span>功能测试</span>\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"adv-menu-item\" data-test=\"limit\" onclick=\"selectAdvTest('limit')\">\n                    <span class=\"menu-icon\">📐</span>\n                    <span>限位测试</span>\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"adv-menu-item\" data-test=\"speed\" onclick=\"selectAdvTest('speed')\">\n                    <span class=\"menu-icon\">⚡</span>\n                    <span>速度测试</span>\n                </button>\n                <button class=\"adv-menu-item\" data-test=\"stream\" onclick=\"selectAdvTest('stream')\">\n                    <span class=\"menu-icon\">📡</span>\n                    <span>推流/存储</span>\n                </button>\n            </div>"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\web\\includes\\advanced.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":95899,"output":608,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96507,"cost":{"input":0.095899,"output":0.0019456000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0978446}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780517793088,"responseId":"cht000d96e0@dx19e8f217e72b958402"}}
