{"type":"message","id":"d5070c46","parentId":"d40a6c0e","timestamp":"2026-06-03T20:19:23.863Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**开发完成汇报 ✅**\n\n---\n\n## 最终完成状态\n\n### 后端模块 ✅\n\n```\nastrohub/calibrate/\n├── core/\n│   ├── coordinates.py      # RA/DEC ↔ Alt/Az 坐标转换\n│   ├── star_catalog.py     # 50颗亮星星表\n│   ├── plate_solve.py      # ASTAP 调用封装\n│   └── model.py            # T-Point 误差模型\n├── calibration_manual.py   # 方案一：手动对准恒星\n├── calibration_auto.py     # 方案二：自动解析\n├── calibration_store.py    # 结果存储\n├── router.py               # REST API (15个端点)\n└── test_all.py             # 测试脚本\n```\n\n### 前端集成 ✅\n\n- 高级功能页面添加\"🌟 天文校准\"入口\n- 支持手动/自动两种校准模式\n- 推荐校准星显示\n- 实时状态反馈\n\n### API 端点\n\n| 端点 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| `POST /api/v1/calibrate/start` | 开始校准 |\n| `GET /api/v1/calibrate/stars/recommended` | 推荐校准星 |\n| `POST /api/v1/calibrate/select_star` | 选择恒星 |\n| `POST /api/v1/calibrate/record` | 记录校准点 |\n| `POST /api/v1/calibrate/capture` | 拍摄解析 |\n| `POST /api/v1/calibrate/compute` | 计算参数 |\n| `POST /api/v1/calibrate/save` | 保存结果 |\n\n### 使用方法\n\n1. 进入高级功能页面\n2. 点击\"🌟 天文校准\"\n3. 选择校准模式（手动/自动）\n4. 按提示完成 4-5 个校准点采集\n5. 点击\"计算参数\"\n6. 保存校准结果"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":103156,"output":433,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103589,"cost":{"input":0.103156,"output":0.0013856,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1045416}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780517950279,"responseId":"cht000fafbb@dx19e8f23db72b8ab592"}}
