{"type":"message","id":"1283b041","parentId":"a05ae550","timestamp":"2026-06-04T06:00:31.870Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了，需要完整的星点对齐算法（XY + 旋转）。让我详细设计：\n\n---\n\n## 完整算法设计\n\n### 一、问题定义\n\nPTZ 在采集多帧过程中可能有：\n- **XY 平移**：轻微抖动、机械震动\n- **旋转**：PTZ 转动微小偏差\n- **缩放**：通常忽略（PTZ 焦距固定）\n\n**目标**：检测每帧相对于参考帧的变换，对齐后再叠加\n\n---\n\n### 二、变换模型\n\n```\n参考帧 → 当前帧的变换:\n\n[x', y'] = [cos(θ) * x - sin(θ) * y + tx,\n            sin(θ) * x + cos(θ) * y + ty]\n\n参数:\n- θ: 旋转角度\n- tx: X 方向平移\n- ty: Y 方向平移\n```\n\n---\n\n### 三、检测方法对比\n\n| 方法 | 适用场景 | 精度 | 计算量 |\n|------|---------|------|--------|\n| **相位相关** | 纯平移 | 高 | 低 |\n| **特征点匹配** | 平移+旋转 | 中 | 中 |\n| **星点匹配** | 天文图像 | 最高 | 高 |\n| **ECC 算法** | 通用 | 高 | 高 |\n\n**推荐：星点匹配法**（天文专用，精度最高）\n\n---\n\n### 四、星点对齐算法流程\n\n```\nStep 1: 检测星点\n    - 参考帧: 检测星点列表 A = [(x1,y1,b1), (x2,y2,b2), ...]\n    - 当前帧: 棟测星点列表 B = [(x1',y1',b1'), ...]\n\nStep 2: 星点匹配\n    - 找到 A 和 B 中对应的星点对\n    - 方法: 最近邻匹配 + 三角形匹配\n\nStep 3: 计算变换参数\n    - 用匹配的星点对计算 (θ, tx, ty)\n\nStep 4: 应用变换\n    - 对当前帧应用变换，对齐到参考帧\n\nStep 5: 叠加\n    - 累加对齐后的帧\n```\n\n---\n\n### 五、详细算法\n\n#### 5.1 星点检测\n\n```python\ndef detect_stars(image, threshold=5, min_area=3):\n    \"\"\"\n    检测图像中的星点\n    \n    Args:\n        image: 灰度图像\n        threshold: 检测阈值（相对于背景的标准差倍数）\n        min_area: 最小星点面积\n    \n    Returns:\n        星点列表 [(x, y, brightness, radius), ...]\n    \"\"\"\n    import cv2\n    import numpy as np\n    \n    # 背景估计\n    background = cv2.medianBlur(image, 15)\n    \n    # 残差图像\n    residual = image.astype(np.float32) - background.astype(np.float32)\n    \n    # 阈值检测\n    std = np.std(residual)\n    mask = residual > threshold * std\n    \n    # 连通域分析\n    num_labels, labels, stats, centroids = cv2.connectedComponentsWithStats(\n        mask.astype(np.uint8)\n    )\n    \n    stars = []\n    for i in range(1, num_labels):  # 跳过背景\n        area = stats[i, cv2.CC_STAT_AREA]\n        if area < min_area:\n            continue\n        \n        x = centroids[i, 0]\n        y = centroids[i, 1]\n        brightness = np.max(residual[labels == i])\n        \n        # 计算星点半径（近似）\n        radius = np.sqrt(area / np.pi)\n        \n        stars.append((x, y, brightness, radius))\n    \n    # 按亮度排序\n    stars.sort(key=lambda s: s[2], reverse=True)\n    \n    return stars\n```\n\n#### 5.2 星点匹配 - 三角形法\n\n```python\ndef match_stars(stars_A, stars_B, tolerance=0.02):\n    \"\"\"\n    匹配两帧的星点（三角形法）\n    \n    原理:\n    - 用最亮的 3 颗星构建三角形\n    - 三角形的边长比在旋转/平移下不变\n    - 匹配三角形，确定星点对应关系\n    \n    Args:\n        stars_A: 参考帧星点\n        stars_B: 当前帧星点\n        tolerance: 边长比容差\n    \n    Returns:\n        匹配对列表 [(idx_A, idx_B), ...]\n    \"\"\"\n    import numpy as np\n    \n    # 取最亮的 N 颗星\n    N = min(20, len(stars_A), len(stars_B))\n    top_A = stars_A[:N]\n    top_B = stars_B[:N]\n    \n    # 构建三角形集合\n    triangles_A = build_triangles(top_A)\n    triangles_B = build_triangles(top_B)\n    \n    # 匹配三角形\n    matched_pairs = []\n    \n    for tri_A in triangles_A:\n        for tri_B in triangles_B:\n            # 计算边长比\n            ratios_A = tri_A['ratios']\n            ratios_B = tri_B['ratios']\n            \n            # 比较边长比\n            diff = np.abs(ratios_A - ratios_B)\n            if np.max(diff) < tolerance:\n                # 找到匹配三角形\n                # 三角形的三个顶点对应\n                for i in range(3):\n                    idx_A = tri_A['indices'][i]\n                    idx_B = tri_B['indices'][i]\n                    matched_pairs.append((idx_A, idx_B))\n                \n                return matched_pairs  # 找到一组匹配即可\n    \n    return matched_pairs\n\n\ndef build_triangles(stars):\n    \"\"\"\n    构建三角形集合\n    \n    用前 N 颗星，每 3 颗构建一个三角形\n    \"\"\"\n    import numpy as np\n    \n    triangles = []\n    n = len(stars)\n    \n    # 用前 10 颗星构建三角形\n    for i in range(min(10, n)):\n        for j in range(i+1, min(10, n)):\n            for k in range(j+1, min(10, n)):\n                # 三点坐标\n                p1 = np.array([stars[i][0], stars[i][1]])\n                p2 = np.array([stars[j][0], stars[j][1]])\n                p3 = np.array([stars[k][0], stars[k][1]])\n                \n                # 三条边长\n                d12 = np.linalg.norm(p1 - p2)\n                d23 = np.linalg.norm(p2 - p3)\n                d31 = np.linalg.norm(p3 - p1)\n                \n                # 边长比（按从小到大排序）\n                sides = np.array([d12, d23, d31])\n                sides.sort()\n                \n                # 归一化（除以最长边）\n                if sides[2] > 0:\n                    ratios = sides / sides[2]\n                else:\n                    continue\n                \n                triangles.append({\n                    'indices': [i, j, k],\n                    'ratios': ratios,\n                    'points': [p1, p2, p3],\n                })\n    \n    return triangles\n```\n\n#### 5.3 计算变换参数\n\n```python\ndef compute_transform(matched_pairs, stars_A, stars_B):\n    \"\"\"\n    计算变换参数\n    \n    Args:\n        matched_pairs: 匹配的星点对 [(idx_A, idx_B), ...]\n        stars_A: 参考帧星点\n        stars_B: 当前帧星点\n    \n    Returns:\n        {'theta': 旋转角度, 'tx': X平移, 'ty': Y平移, 'matrix': 变换矩阵}\n    \"\"\"\n    import numpy as np\n    \n    if len(matched_pairs) < 3:\n        # 匹配点太少，使用相位相关法\n        return None\n    \n    # 构建点集\n    points_A = []\n    points_B = []\n    \n    for idx_A, idx_B in matched_pairs[:10]:  # 最多用 10 对\n        points_A.append([stars_A[idx_A][0], stars_A[idx_A][1]])\n        points_B.append([stars_B[idx_B][0], stars_B[idx_B][1]])\n    \n    points_A = np.array(points_A, dtype=np.float32)\n    points_B = np.array(points_B, dtype=np.float32)\n    \n    # 使用 OpenCV 的 estimateAffinePartial2D\n    # 可估计: 旋转 + 平移 + 缩放（如果需要）\n    import cv2\n    \n    matrix, inliers = cv2.estimateAffinePartial2D(\n        points_B,  # 源点（当前帧）\n        points_A,  # 目标点（参考帧）\n        method=cv2.RANSAC,\n        ransacReprojThreshold=3.0,\n    )\n    \n    if matrix is None:\n        return None\n    \n    # 从矩阵提取参数\n    # matrix = [[cos(θ), -sin(θ), tx],\n    #           [sin(θ),  cos(θ), ty]]\n    \n    cos_theta = matrix[0, 0]\n    sin_theta = matrix[1, 0]\n    \n    theta = np.arctan2(sin_theta, cos_theta)  # 弧度\n    tx = matrix[0, 2]\n    ty = matrix[1, 2]\n    \n    return {\n        'theta': np.degrees(theta),  # 角度\n        'tx': tx,\n        'ty': ty,\n        'matrix': matrix,\n    }\n```\n\n#### 5.4 应用变换\n\n```python\ndef apply_transform(image, matrix):\n    \"\"\"\n    应用变换矩阵\n    \n    Args:\n        image: 原始图像\n        matrix: 2x3 变换矩阵\n    \n    Returns:\n        对齐后的图像\n    \"\"\"\n    import cv2\n    \n    h, w = image.shape[:2]\n    \n    aligned = cv2.warpAffine(\n        image,\n        matrix,\n        (w, h),\n        flags=cv2.INTER_LINEAR,\n        borderMode=cv2.BORDER_CONSTANT,\n        borderValue=0,\n    )\n    \n    return aligned\n```\n\n#### 5.5 叠加算法\n\n```python\ndef stack_frames(frames_aligned, method='mean'):\n    \"\"\"\n    叠加对齐后的帧\n    \n    Args:\n        frames_aligned: 对齐后的帧列表\n        method: 叠加方法 ('mean', 'median', 'sigma_clip')\n    \n    Returns:\n        叠加结果 (32-bit float)\n    \"\"\"\n    import numpy as np\n    \n    # 转换为 float32 数组\n    stack = np.array([f.astype(np.float32) for f in frames_aligned])\n    \n    if method == 'mean':\n        result = np.mean(stack, axis=0)\n    \n    elif method == 'median':\n        result = np.median(stack, axis=0)\n    \n    elif method == 'sigma_clip':\n        # Sigma clipping\n        # 对每个像素，剔除偏离 > 3σ 的值\n        mean = np.mean(stack, axis=0)\n        std = np.std(stack, axis=0)\n        \n        # 创建掩码\n        mask = np.abs(stack - mean) <= 3 * std\n        \n        # 应用掩码后的均值\n        result = np.sum(stack * mask, axis=0) / np.sum(mask, axis=0)\n    \n    return result\n```\n\n---\n\n### 六、完整流程\n\n```python\ndef process_stack(video_stream, target_exposure, method='sigma_clip'):\n    \"\"\"\n    完整叠加流程\n    \n    Args:\n        video_stream: PTZ 视频流\n        target_exposure: 目标等效曝光 (2, 5, 10, 30 秒)\n        method: 叠加方法\n    \n    Returns:\n        叠加结果图像\n    \"\"\"\n    # 计算需要的帧数\n    base_fps = 10  # PTZ 帧率\n    frame_count = target_exposure * base_fps\n    \n    # 采集帧\n    frames = capture_frames(video_stream, frame_count)\n    \n    # 检测参考帧星点\n    ref_stars = detect_stars(frames[0])\n    \n    # 对齐每帧\n    frames_aligned = [frames[0]]  # 参考帧\n    \n    for frame in frames[1:]:\n        # 棟测当前帧星点\n        cur_stars = detect_stars(frame)\n        \n        # 匹配星点\n        matched = match_stars(ref_stars, cur_stars)\n        \n        # 计算变换\n        if matched:\n            transform = compute_transform(matched, ref_stars, cur_stars)\n            if transform:\n                aligned = apply_transform(frame, transform['matrix'])\n            else:\n                aligned = frame  # 无法对齐，使用原图\n        else:\n            aligned = frame  # 无法匹配，使用原图\n        \n        frames_aligned.append(aligned)\n    \n    # 叠加\n    result = stack_frames(frames_aligned, method)\n    \n    # 输出 FITS\n    save_fits(result, target_exposure, frame_count)\n    \n    return result\n```\n\n---\n\n### 七、边界情况处理\n\n| 问题 | 解决方案 |\n|------|---------|\n| 星点太少 (<5) | 使用相位相关法 |\n| 三角形匹配失败 | 用最亮星的坐标直接匹配 |\n| 变换矩阵异常 | 检查旋转角 <5°，平移 <50px |\n| 帧质量差（云遮挡） | 检测星点数，跳过该帧 |\n\n---\n\n### 八、代码文件结构\n\n```\nastrohub/stack/\n├── __init__.py\n├── detect.py          # 星点检测\n├── match.py           # 星点匹配（三角形法）\n├── transform.py       # 变换计算和应用\n├── stack.py           # 叠加算法\n├── fits_writer.py     # FITS 输出\n├── process.py         # 完整流程\n└── router.py          # API\n```\n\n---\n\n**老板，需要我开始编写完整代码吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":108804,"output":3072,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111876,"cost":{"input":0.108804,"output":0.009830400000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1186344}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780552754186,"responseId":"cht000d3862@dx19e9136edf5b8aa822"}}
