{"type":"message","id":"610bb45c","parentId":"abd3031a","timestamp":"2026-06-04T06:03:28.872Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，我先搜索成熟的天文图像叠加对齐方法，对比最佳实践。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_55f25be518344376a0951a1f","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"context":"isolated","mode":"run","runtime":"subagent","task":"搜索天文图像叠加对齐的最佳实践方法，重点关注：\n\n1. **星点检测算法**：\n   - DAOphot\n   - SExtractor\n   - OpenCV 方法\n   - 对比精度和性能\n\n2. **图像对齐方法**：\n   - 星点匹配（三角形法、模式匹配）\n   - 相位相关法\n   - ECC (Enhanced Correlation Coefficient)\n   - 光流法\n   - AstroPy/astroalign 库\n\n3. **叠加算法**：\n   - Mean/Median\n   - Sigma Clipping\n   - Winsorized Mean\n   - 对比噪声抑制效果\n\n4. **成熟软件参考**：\n   - DeepSkyStacker\n   - PixInsight\n   - SiriL\n   - ASTAP 内置叠加\n\n5. **Python 库**：\n   - astroalign\n   - reproject\n   - ccdproc\n   - astropy\n\n输出：\n- 各方法的优缺点对比表\n- 推荐的 Python 实现方案\n- 关键参数设置建议"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":112113,"output":271,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112384,"cost":{"input":0.11211299999999999,"output":0.0008672,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.11298019999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780552978591,"responseId":"cht000db054@dx19e913a72c7b85f532"}}
