{"type":"message","id":"a9e09998","parentId":"b4b6f1fc","timestamp":"2026-06-04T08:19:20.563Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 完成汇报 ✅\n\n### 已完成\n\n1. **需求文档**：`documents/live_stack_requirements.md`\n   - 页面布局调整（主控台 Live View + 高级功能 WASM 单独）\n   - Live Stack 核心需求\n   - 硬件曝光时间处理\n\n2. **Live Stack 模块**：`stack/live_stack.py`\n   - Running Mean 实时累加\n   - XY + 旋转对齐（astroalign 三角形法，降级相位相关）\n   - 硬件曝光时间参数\n   - 实时预览输出\n\n### 测试结果\n\n```\nLive Stack 测试通过 ✅\n- 20 帧叠加成功\n- FITS + JPG 输出成功\n- 对齐方法: 相位相关（无 astroalign 时降级）\n```\n\n### 待完成\n\n- `live_view.py`：前端 Live View 视图控制\n- 主控台 UI 集成\n- 高级功能 WASM 单独入口\n\n**老板，需要继续完成 live_view.py 和前端集成吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":147062,"output":240,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":147302,"cost":{"input":0.147062,"output":0.000768,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.14783}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780561127702,"responseId":"cht000dcb7e@dx19e91b6c40fb828282"}}
{"type":"message","id":"73df2426","parentId":"a9e09998","timestamp":"2026-06-04T08:19:26.316Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"telegram:8447197723\",\n  \"message_id\": \"31375\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"sender\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-06-04 16:11 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Yixing Zhang (8447197723)\",\n  \"id\": \"8447197723\",\n  \"name\": \"Yixing Zhang\",\n  \"username\": \"ZhangyixingTG\"\n}\n```\n\n默认不保存视频和图像实施叠加的图像，在内存里处理。如有必要再创建livestack的文件夹，用于临时数据。"}],"timestamp":1780561166311}}
{"type":"message","id":"8cb37e33","parentId":"73df2426","timestamp":"2026-06-04T08:20:21.632Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来创建 `live_view.py` 并修改默认不保存中间叠加图像。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-5d0da65296634d4c99acd250b5374f05","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\nLive View 模块 - 实时预览控制\n\n提供 Live Stack 的实时预览功能，用于主控台和高级功能页面。\n\nAuthor: 雅痞张@南方天文\n\"\"\"\n\nimport numpy as np\nimport cv2\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom typing import Optional, Callable\n\n\nclass LiveView:\n    \"\"\"\n    Live View 实时预览控制器\n    \n    功能：\n    - 实时显示叠加进度\n    - 生成预览 JPG（不保存中间帧）\n    - 提供预览图像给前端\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        preview_interval: int = 10,  # 每 N 帧更新预览\n        output_dir: str = \"stack/output\",\n    ):\n        \"\"\"\n        初始化 Live View\n        \n        Args:\n            preview_interval: 预览刷新间隔（帧数）\n            output_dir: 最终输出目录\n        \"\"\"\n        self.preview_interval = preview_interval\n        self.output_dir = output_dir\n        \n        # 预览状态\n        self.preview_image = None\n        self.last_preview_time = None\n        self.frame_count = 0\n    \n    def update_preview(\n        self,\n        stacked_image: np.ndarray,\n        frame_count: int,\n        target_frames: int,\n        callback: Optional[Callable] = None,\n    ) -> Optional[np.ndarray]:\n        \"\"\"\n        更新预览图像\n        \n        Args:\n            stacked_image: 当前叠加结果\n            frame_count: 已叠加帧数\n            target_frames: 目标帧数\n            callback: 预览回调函数\n        \n        Returns:\n            8-bit 预览图像 (用于前端显示)\n        \"\"\"\n        self.frame_count = frame_count\n        \n        # 检查是否需要刷新预览\n        if frame_count % self.preview_interval != 0 and frame_count != target_frames:\n            return None\n        \n        # 生成预览图\n        preview_8bit = self._create_preview(stacked_image)\n        self.preview_image = preview_8bit\n        self.last_preview_time = datetime.now()\n        \n        # 回调\n        if callback:\n            callback(preview_8bit, frame_count, target_frames)\n        \n        return preview_8bit\n    \n    def _create_preview(self, image: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n        \"\"\"\n        创建 8-bit 预览图\n        \n        使用百分位拉伸增强对比度\n        \"\"\"\n        if image is None:\n            return None\n        \n        img = image.astype(np.float64)\n        \n        # 百分位拉伸\n        vmin = np.percentile(img, 1)\n        vmax = np.percentile(img, 99)\n        \n        if vmax - vmin < 1e-6:\n            return np.zeros_like(image, dtype=np.uint8)\n        \n        # 拉伸\n        img_scaled = (img - vmin) / (vmax - vmin)\n        img_scaled = np.clip(img_scaled, 0, 1)\n        \n        # 8-bit\n        preview = (img_scaled * 255).astype(np.uint8)\n        \n        return preview\n    \n    def get_preview_base64(self) -> Optional[str]:\n        \"\"\"\n        获取预览图的 base64 编码（用于前端显示）\n        \n        Returns:\n            base64 编码的 JPG 图像\n        \"\"\"\n        if self.preview_image is None:\n            return None\n        \n        # 编码为 JPG\n        success, buffer = cv2.imencode('.jpg', self.preview_image, [cv2.IMWRITE_JPEG_QUALITY, 85])\n        \n        if not success:\n            return None\n        \n        # Base64\n        import base64\n        b64 = base64.b64encode(buffer).decode('utf-8')\n        \n        return f\"data:image/jpeg;base64,{b64}\"\n    \n    def get_status(self) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        获取预览状态\n        \"\"\"\n        return {\n            'frame_count': self.frame_count,\n            'has_preview': self.preview_image is not None,\n            'last_update': self.last_preview_time.isoformat() if self.last_preview_time else None,\n        }\n\n\n# 模块测试\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    print(\"Live View 模块测试\")\n    \n    live_view = LiveView(preview_interval=5)\n    \n    # 模拟叠加过程\n    stacked = np.zeros((100, 100), dtype=np.float32)\n    \n    for i in range(1, 21):\n        # 模拟添加帧\n        frame = np.random.rand(100, 100) * 100\n        stacked = stacked * (i - 1) / i + frame / i\n        \n        # 更新预览\n        preview = live_view.update_preview(stacked, i, 20)\n        \n        if preview is not None:\n            print(f\"  帧 {i}: 预览已更新\")\n    \n    # 获取状态\n    status = live_view.get_status()\n    print(f\"\\n状态: {status}\")\n    \n    # Base64 测试\n    b64 = live_view.get_preview_base64()\n    print(f\"Base64 长度: {len(b64) if b64 else 0}\")\n    \n    print(\"\\n测试完成\")","path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\stack\\live_view.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":147481,"output":1149,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":148630,"cost":{"input":0.147481,"output":0.0036768000000000005,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1511578}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780561166316,"responseId":"cht000dffbb@dx19e91b75f58b958402"}}
