{"type":"message","id":"b0a8554d","parentId":"941019e9","timestamp":"2026-06-04T08:57:49.082Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"更新 HEARTBEAT："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-3d37e57fffc146cbaabfe29c1ae91f6f","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"### 当前任务\n- Live Stack 模块已完成\n- 前端集成已完成\n- 待验收\n\n### Live Stack 集成（已完成 ✅）\n| # | 项目 | 结果 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | stack/router.py API | ✅ 7个端点 |\n| 2 | main.py 路由注册 | ✅ |\n| 3 | console.html 控制栏 | ✅ |\n| 4 | index.html JS函数 | ✅ start/stop/save |","oldText":"### 当前任务\n- 天文校准模块已完成\n- 图像叠加模块已完成\n- 待老板验收"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":159898,"output":197,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":160095,"cost":{"input":0.15989799999999998,"output":0.0006304,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1605284}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780563419846,"responseId":"cht000da824@dx19e91d9b839ba29112"}}
