{"type":"message","id":"51a50cb1","parentId":"d2e82e23","timestamp":"2026-06-04T09:44:17.900Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"追加 Live Stack 技术要点："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a01074f3c2ab4cd4bd998f7d","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"### ⚠️ 设备状态检测陷阱\n- `wait_stable()` 只检测\"位置是否稳定\"，不检测\"位置是否正确\"\n- 正确做法：先 `goto_preset(10)` → 等待5秒 → 验证位置\n- **稳定验证必须包含位置准确性检查**（连续20点0误差）\n\n### ⚠️ Live Stack 关键规则\n- **禁止保存中间叠加图像**：Running Mean 仅在内存处理\n- **对齐必须包含旋转**：astroalign 三角形法（支持旋转）\n- **算法选择**：Running Mean (O(1) 内存) 而非 Sigma Clipping (O(N帧))\n- **硬件曝光时间**：需从 PTZ 设备获取或用户配置\n- **帧数计算**：N = target_exposure / hardware_exposure\n\n### ⚠️ 端口配置（最高优先级）\n- **AstroHub 正式服务**: 10280\n- **摄像头 ISAPI**: 80\n- **摄像头 WebSocket**: 7681\n- **禁止自创端口**：测试脚本必须使用 10280","oldText":"### ⚠️ 设备状态检测陷阱\n- `wait_stable()` 只检测\"位置是否稳定\"，不检测\"位置是否正确\"\n- 正确做法：先 `goto_preset(10)` → 等待5秒 → 验证位置\n- **稳定验证必须包含位置准确性检查**（连续20点0误差）"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":49088,"output":387,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49475,"cost":{"input":0.049088,"output":0.0012384000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0503264}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780566236590,"responseId":"cht000d1c45@dx19e9204a859b958302"}}
