{"type":"message","id":"61975112","parentId":"29f944a6","timestamp":"2026-06-04T09:44:48.512Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 复盘与记忆更新完成 ✅\n\n### 已更新文件\n\n| 文件 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| `.learnings/REVIEW_20260604.md` | 完整复盘记录 |\n| `.learnings/ERRORS.md` | 新增 4 条错误记录 |\n| `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md` | 新增 4 条教训 |\n| `MEMORY.md` | 新增 Live Stack 关键规则 |\n| `HEARTBEAT.md` | 更新完成状态 |\n\n### 关键教训总结\n\n```\n✅ 禁止自创端口 → 必须使用 10280\n✅ Live Stack 对齐必须包含旋转\n✅ Live Stack 默认仅在内存处理\n✅ Running Mean 是实时叠加首选算法\n✅ FITS Header 必填 EXPTIME/NFRAMES/DATE-OBS/STACKMETH\n```\n\n### 下一步\n\n1. PTZ 跟踪算法开发\n2. 安装 astroalign + photutils\n3. 硬件曝光时间获取确认\n4. 前端预览优化"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":48632,"output":238,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48870,"cost":{"input":0.048631999999999995,"output":0.0007616000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.049393599999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780566273586,"responseId":"cht000d264d@dx19e92053f33b958302"}}
