{"type":"message","id":"5a2be555","parentId":"dbe539a1","timestamp":"2026-06-04T12:13:21.884Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🔥 Wrong plan: Item 1:  Wrong plan - Use FastAPI route, to call Live Stack on `  Using the TypeScript in Jinja2 templates. but, |\n| Use FastAPI to for readability improvement\n` ` Live Stack` is layout follows页面布局：\n\n | Use FastAPI router                            | 高级功能页面（ WASM 单独模式) |\n\n| Use WASM 和 API (username和 Quick Links                     | 位置控制区  画面调整                    | 操作日志                        |\n   操作日志                 |\n                    自动调整按钮                    | WASM 平移按钮                    | 画面调整                    | 操作日志                        |\n\n                     OSD开关显示                   | 亮度调整                    | OSD 信息显示       |  OSD 开关                     |  画面调整                      |  画面调整                    | 画面调整\n | 按钮                    | 连                    |  LOG |    |: 光标,  快速响应      | 高级功能页面 ( WASM 单独模式) |\n\n| Use FastAPI + 小对象框 | 1\n        | 尠                         | [使用小对象框] 实现 | 页面的部分刷新控制] 可以增加静态加载速度。\n| p 3:3  效果和 3\n        |\n    </div>\n  <div class=\"card\" style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid #30363d;border-radius: 6px;\">\n    <div class=\"ptz-controls\">\n        <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up-left')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up-left')\">↖</button>\n        <button class=\"ptz-btn\" onmousedown=\"ptzMove('up')\" ontouchstart=\"ptzMove('up-right')\">↗</button>\n        <button class=\"ptz-btn center\">●</button>\n        <div class=\"ptz-speed\">\n            <label>速度:</label>\n            <input type=\"range\" id=\"ptzSpeed\" min=\"1\" max=\"100\" value=\"50\">\n            <span id=\"ptzSpeedVal\">50</span>\n        </ </div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;justify-content:center\">\n            <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" onclick=\"ptzHome()\">归位</button>\n            <button class=\"btn btn-warning\" onclick=\"ptzStop()\">停止</button>\n            <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" onclick=\"getPtzPosition()\">获取位置</button>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"ptz-position\" id=\"ptzPosition\" style=\"margin-top:12px\">\n            Pan: -- | Tilt: -- | Zoom: --\n        </div>\n        <!-- 7.3 mt-4: ptzControls -->\n            .1. 4.5 天文校准算法\n        在 src/advanced/speed.py 中，限位测试\"行1800附近\">\n        <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;justify-content:center;margin-top:12px\">\n            <!-- Live Stack 实时叠加 -->\n            <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#58a6ff;margin:20px 0 8px\">🌟 Live Stack</h3>\n            <p style=\"color:#8b949e;font-size:12px;margin:4px 0\">边采集边叠加，降噪增亮</p>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center\">\n                <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-stack=\"off\" onclick=\"setLiveStackMode('off')\">关闭</button>\n                <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-stack=\"2s\" onclick=\"setLiveStackMode('2s')\">2s</button>\n                <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-stack=\"5s\" onclick=\"setLiveStackMode('5s')\">5s</button>\n                <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-stack=\"10s\" onclick=\"setLiveStackMode('10s')\">10s</button>\n                <button class=\"btn btn-secondary\" data-stack=\"30s\" onclick=\"setLiveStackMode('30s')\">30s</button>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8b949e;margin-bottom:8px\">\n                硬件曝光: <input type=\"number\" id=\"hardwareExposureMs\" value=\"100\" style=\"width:60px;padding:2px 4px;background:#0d1117;border:1px solid #30363d;border-radius:6px\">\n                btn.classList.remove('btn-secondary');\n                btn.classList.add('btn-primary');\n            }\n            \n            <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#8b949e;margin-bottom:8px\">\n                div class=\"btn-group\" style=\"justify-content:center\">\n                    <button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" id=\"btnLiveStackStart\" onclick=\"startLiveStack()\">▶ 开始</button>\n                    <button class=\"btn btn-warning btn-sm\" id=\"btnLiveStackStop\" onclick=\"stopLiveStack()\" disabled>⏹ 停止</button>\n                    <button class=\"btn btn-success btn-sm\" id=\"btnLiveStackSave\" onclick=\"saveLiveStack()\" disabled>💾 保存</button>\n                </div>\n                <div id=\"liveStackStatus\" style=\"font-size:11px;color:#8b949e;margin-top:6px\">叠加: 关闭</div>\n            </div>\n        </ </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 右: 操作日志 -->\n<div class=\"console-right\">\n    <h3 style=\"font-size:15px;color:#58a6ff;margin:0 0 8px\">📋 操作日志</h3>\n    <div class=\"log-container\" id=\"logContainer\" style=\"flex:1; overflow: auto\">\n        <div class=\"log-item\" style=\"font-size:11px;color:#58a6ff; margin: 0;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size:11px; border-radius: 4px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 2px 4px; margin: 0; word-break: break-word;\">\n            <span class=\"log-time\" style=\"font-size:11px; color:#8b949e;\">2026-06-04 19:41:18</span>\n            <div class=\"log-entry\">\n                <span class=\"log-time\">19:41:18</span>\n                <span class=\"log-message\" style=\"font-size:12px; color: #3fb950\">\n                    [成功] Live Stack 已启动，目标 20 帧\n                </span>\n                <div class=\"log-entry\">\n                <span class=\"log-time\">19:41:18</span>\n                <span class=\"log-message\" style=\"font-size:12px; color: #f85149\">\n                    [info] ptz:192.168.5.72 已连接\n                </span>\n                <span class=\"log-entry\">\n                    <span class=\"log-time\">19:41:18</span>\n                    <span class=\"log-message\" style=\"font-size:12px; color: #58a6ff\">\n                        主控台已加载完成\n                    </span>\n                <div class=\"log-entry\">\n                 