{"type":"message","id":"3e3986f5","parentId":"ba9afd96","timestamp":"2026-06-07T19:18:05.079Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3e08cc6427554a6595ecf0cf","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        \"\"\"添加一帧\"\"\"\n        if not self.is_running:\n            return {'success': False, 'message': '未启动'}\n        \n        frame_float = frame.astype(np.float32)\n        \n        # 第一帧作为参考\n        if self.reference_frame is None:\n            self.reference_frame = frame_float\n            self.running_mean = frame_float.copy()\n            self.frame_count = 1\n            \n            return {\n                'success': True,\n                'frame_count': 1,\n                'is_reference': True,\n            }\n        \n        # 对齐\n        aligned = self._align_frame(frame_float)\n        \n        # Running Mean\n        self.frame_count += 1\n        alpha = 1.0 / self.frame_count\n        self.running_mean = self.running_mean * (1 - alpha) + aligned * alpha\n        \n        return {\n            'success': True,\n            'frame_count': self.frame_count,\n            'progress': self.frame_count / self.target_frames,\n        }\n    \n    def _align_frame(self, frame: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n        \"\"\"对齐帧 (XY + 旋转)\"\"\"\n        if HAS_ASTROALIGN:\n            try:\n                aligned, _ = aa.register(frame, self.reference_frame)\n                return aligned\n            except Exception:\n                pass\n        \n        # 降级：相位相关 (仅平移)\n        result = cv2.phaseCorrelate(self.reference_frame.astype(np.float32), \n                                    frame.astype(np.float32))\n        shift_x, shift_y = result[0][0], result[0][1]\n        \n        M = np.array([[1, 0, -shift_x], [0, 1, -shift_y]], dtype=np.float32)\n        h, w = frame.shape[:2]\n        aligned = cv2.warpAffine(frame, M, (w, h))\n        \n        return aligned\n    \n    def finish(self, basename: Optional[str] = None, save_output: bool = True) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"完成叠加\n        \n        Args:\n            basename: 输出文件名基础\n            save_output: 是否保存输出文件（默认 True）\n        \"\"\"\n        self.is_running = False\n        \n        if self.frame_count < 1 or self.running_mean is None:\n            return {'success': False, 'message': '无帧数据'}\n        \n        # 仅在需要保存时创建输出\n        if save_output:\n            if self.writer is None:\n                self.writer = OutputWriter(output_dir=self.output_dir)\n            \n            if not basename:\n                basename = f\"live_stack_{datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d_%H%M%S')}\"\n            \n            output = self.writer.save(\n                image=self.running_mean,\n                basename=basename,\n                exposure_time=self.target_exposure,\n                n_frames=self.frame_count,\n            )\n            \n            return {\n\n[97 more lines in file. Use offset=160 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780859885079}}
{"type":"message","id":"cbdf755e","parentId":"3e3986f5","timestamp":"2026-06-07T19:18:47.192Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 回答老板问题\n\n**当前算法不计算旋转速度，而是直接检测每帧的旋转角度并对齐。**\n\n### 算法逻辑\n\n```\n帧N → 星点检测 → 与参考帧匹配 → 计算变换矩阵 → 对齐 → Running Mean累加\n```\n\n### 旋转处理方式\n\n| 方法 | 原理 | 输出 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **astroalign** | 三角形法星点匹配 | 旋转角度 + 平移量 |\n| **相位相关（降级）** | FFT 相关 | 仅平移量（无旋转） |\n\n### astroalign 返回的变换信息\n\n```python\ntransf = aa.find_transform(frame, reference_frame)\ntransf.rotation  # 旋转角度（弧度）\ntransf.translation  # XY平移量\ntransf.scale  # 缩放因子\n```\n\n---\n\n**关键点**：算法不预测旋转速度，而是**逐帧检测实际旋转量**并补偿。\n\n如果老板需要计算旋转速度（用于 PTZ 跟踪），需要额外开发：\n1. 记录每帧变换历史\n2. 计算旋转角度变化率（度/秒）\n3. 映射到 PTZ 速度指令\n\n**老板需要旋转速度计算功能吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":61717,"output":279,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61996,"cost":{"input":0.061716999999999994,"output":0.0008928000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0626098}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780859885081,"responseId":"cht000ef8a4@dx19ea385584eb87e242"}}
