{"type":"message","id":"e60bd305","parentId":"82df2f71","timestamp":"2026-06-10T15:55:50.413Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 复盘完成 ✅\n\n### 已更新文件\n\n| 文件 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| `documents/ALGORITHM_DEVELOPMENT.md` | **算法开发文档**（13000+ 字） |\n| `.learnings/REVIEW_20260610.md` | 复盘记录 |\n| `MEMORY.md` | 重要日期更新 |\n| `HEARTBEAT.md` | 当前任务 + 文档位置 |\n\n### 开发文档内容\n\n```\n1. 图像叠加算法\n   - 星点检测：photutils.DAOStarFinder\n   - 图像对齐：astroalign (XY+旋转)\n   - 叠加算法：Sigma Clipping / Running Mean\n\n2. PTZ 跟踪算法\n   - 恒星跟踪：15°/小时 补偿\n   - 图像引导跟踪：变换历史推算\n   - 速度映射：归一化到 PTZ 档位\n\n3. PTZ 指向算法\n   - 坐标转换：RA/DEC → Alt/Az\n   - T-Point 修正：6 参数模型\n   - PTZ 映射：Pan/Tilt 坐标\n\n4. 天文校准算法\n   - 手动对准方案\n   - 自动 Plate Solve 方案\n```\n\n### 文件位置\n\n**主文档**: `documents/ALGORITHM_DEVELOPMENT.md`\n\n**老板可查阅此文档了解所有算法开发方法。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":70162,"output":317,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70479,"cost":{"input":0.070162,"output":0.0010144000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0711764}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781106870385,"responseId":"cht000d772a@dx19eb23e14feba5e412"}}
